Checks the type of values in the passed dictionary, d, and extends singular
values 1d numpy arrays of length n_sites.

Example:
\>>> d = {"foo": 1, "bar": [6, 7, 8, 9]}
\>>> broadcast_dict_values(d, 4)
{'foo': [1, 1, 1, 1], 'bar': [6, 7, 8, 9]}
